<h1>希</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#990000;">xī</span><span class=alesi>(xi1)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 希 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 希</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/rare" style="color:black;">rare</a>; <a href="/dictionary/hope" style="color:black;">hope</a>, <a href="/dictionary/expect" style="color:black;">expect</a>, strive for</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 7<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 7 strokes: <a href="/character/我" title="wo3: our, us, i, me, my, we">我</a>, <a href="/character/这" title="zhe4: this, the, here">这</a>, <a href="/character/来" title="lai2: come, coming; return, returning">来</a>, <a href="/character/时" title="shi2: time, season; era, age, period">时</a>, <a href="/character/你" title="ni3: you, second person pronoun">你</a>, <a href="/character/作" title="zuo4: make; work; compose, write; act, perform">作</a>, <a href="/character/里" title="li3: unit of distance; village; lane">里</a>, <a href="/character/没" title="mei2: not, have not, none; drown, sink">没</a>, <a href="/character/还" title="hai2: still, yet, also, besides">还</a>, <a href="/character/进" title="jin4: advance, make progress, enter">进</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/巾" title="Kangxi radical 50">巾</a>&nbsp;50.4</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 2 <br><small>Other HSK 2 characters: <a href="/character/房" title="fang2: house, building; room">房</a>, <a href="/character/虽" title="sui1: although, even if">虽</a>, <a href="/character/红" title="hong2: red, vermillion; blush, flush">红</a>, <a href="/character/黑" title="hei1: black; dark; evil, sinister">黑</a>, <a href="/character/考" title="kao3: examine, test; investigate">考</a>, <a href="/character/足" title="zu2: foot; attain, satisfy, enough">足</a>, <a href="/character/孩" title="hai2: baby, child; children">孩</a>, <a href="/character/站" title="zhan4: stand up; a stand, station">站</a>, <a href="/character/吧" title="ba: emphatic final particle">吧</a>, <a href="/character/找" title="zhao3: search, seek, look for; find">找</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-2" title="List of HSK 2 characters" style="white-space: nowrap;">more